{"tid":2072533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗：港區國安法凌駕本地法律　違者監禁3至10年","createTime":"2020-06-20T16:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T16:07:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19204b3fb0aa67bea7ad8d39954a13a93e9240fa","tid":2072533,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:05:18.000Z","msg":"人大常委會法工委負責人就「港區國安法」的說明今日（20日）發布，全國人大常委譚耀宗表示，港區國安法放進《基本法》附件三是中央立法，與香港本地法律層次不同，對本地法律有凌駕性。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，港區國安法下沒有罪行會判終身監禁，草案條文對分裂國家、顛覆國家政權、恐怖活動，以及勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全4類犯罪行為有清晰界定，罰則根據案情輕重決定，案情輕微者監禁3年，其他則監禁5年至10年，與香港刑法相若。"},{"pid":"9d530c2ab8df99e700ece3256a6e0f538ea00dcf","tid":2072533,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:05:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200620/s00001/1592656130593/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200620%2Fs00001%2F1592656130593%2F&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=2a86867a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200620%2Fs00001%2F1592656130593%2F&h=7fec6544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200620/s00001/1592656130593/</a>"},{"pid":"3bc6d405e2a3e09b70d5622ac11f7120e96fa660","tid":2072533,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"let them come<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}